videos.description: Donte Jackson returns a kickoff for a touchdown, but it gets called back due to a holding penalty.
videos.headline: LSU kickoff return TD negated by penalty

videos.description: Derrius Guice run for 4 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Derrius Guice reaches end zone for LSU

videos.description: Eli Jenkins pass complete to Krenwick Sanders for 76 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Jacksonville State strikes back with long TD pass

videos.description: Derrius Guice run for 44 yds to the JaxSt 17 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Guice breaks long run

videos.description: Bry'Kiethon Mouton run for 2 yds for a TD
videos.headline: LSU fullback pushes Tiger lead to double-digits

videos.description: LSU's Tre'Davious White fields the punt and goes backwards to fend off defenders, turns around and takes off for an incredible 60-yard touchdown, putting the Tigers up 27-10.
videos.headline: Tre'Davious White scores on must-see punt return

videos.description: Danny Etling pass intercepted, touchback. Reggie Hall return for no gain
videos.headline: Jacksonville State picks off LSU's Etling

videos.description: Eli Jenkins pass intercepted Donte Jackson return for 39 yds to the JaxSt 45
videos.headline: Tigers force Jacksonville State's first turnover of game

videos.description: Danny Etling run for 2 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Etling takes it himself for LSU score

videos.description: LSU returns home to play their first game since all the flooding in Louisiana, without Leonard Fournette, and beats Jacksonville State 34-13 with the help of a must-see punt return touchdown.
